          <li>Comply with the terms and policies of any third‑party service you use via the App.</li>
          <li>Not use the App to send spam, malware, or unlawful content.</li>
          <li>Keep your accounts, OAuth access, and API keys secure.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>2. Third‑Party Services</h2>
        <p>Depending on the actions you run, QuiKey may integrate with third parties including:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Google (Gmail, Drive, Gemini)</li>
