          <li>You are responsible for obtaining, managing, and safeguarding your API keys and third‑party accounts.</li>
          <li>The App uses your keys/tokens only to communicate with the provider(s) you configure.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>4. Important Safety Notice (Backups and Data Loss)</h2>
        <p>
          The App interacts with files you select and system services you enable. While we aim to be safe and reliable:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>You are responsible for maintaining backups of your files and your system.</li>
          <li>
            Do not use the App in a way that would be unsafe if a file were modified, corrupted, deleted, or uploaded
            unexpectedly.
