          AI-generated output may be inaccurate, incomplete, or inappropriate. Do not rely on AI output as professional
          advice (legal, medical, financial, security, etc.). You are responsible for verifying results before acting on
          them.
        </p>

        <h2>6. Disclaimer of Warranties</h2>
        <p class="all-caps">
