          MERCHANTABILITY, FITNESS FOR A PARTICULAR PURPOSE, AND NON‑INFRINGEMENT. WE DO NOT WARRANT THAT THE APP WILL
          BE ERROR‑FREE, SECURE, OR UNINTERRUPTED.
        </p>

        <h2>7. Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p class="all-caps">
          TO THE MAXIMUM EXTENT PERMITTED BY LAW: (A) WE WILL NOT BE LIABLE FOR ANY INDIRECT, INCIDENTAL, SPECIAL,
          CONSEQUENTIAL, EXEMPLARY, OR PUNITIVE DAMAGES, OR ANY LOSS OF DATA, FILES, PROFITS, REVENUE, OR BUSINESS
